        "timestamp": 1780621848
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> avanhatt created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13550#discussion_r3359758204\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ah, we added uses of <code>cranelift_codegen::isa::aarch64::inst::...</code> within <code>cranelift/isle/veri</code>, which made all of these fail <code>deny(missing_docs)</code>. </p>\n<p>Would we prefer I add an <code>#![allow(missing_docs)]</code> with a comment that we use these within <code>cranelift/isle/veri</code>? Or something else?</p>\n</blockquote>",
